  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct used in posterior lumbar spinal fixation. The model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two independent laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors have been assessed. The intended use is pre-market submission support for a Class II spinal fixation device under 21 CFR 888.3070. One factor (Test conditions) is below the required level due to a single test condition evaluated; all other factors meet or exceed required levels. Decision: Accepted at Medium assurance.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-fea-requirement",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-predicts-f1717-structural-performance",
